'''毕丹星'''（{{lang-en|Pritam Khaira Singh}}；{{lang-pa|ਪ੍ਰੀਤਮ ਸਿੰਘ}}；{{bd|1976年|8月2日}}<ref name="Parliament Profile">{{Cite web|title=MP | Parliament of Singapore|url=https://www.parliament.gov.sg/mps/list-of-current-mps/mp/details/pritam-singh|access-date=2021-12-14|archive-date=2021-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211217120619/https://www.parliament.gov.sg/mps/list-of-current-mps/mp/details/pritam-singh|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是一名[[工人黨_(新加坡)|新加坡工人党]]的政治家和律師，自2011年5月7日起，毕丹星一直是[[新加坡國會|新加坡國會]][[阿裕尼集选区|阿裕尼集選區]]的國會議員 (MP)。<ref>[http://www.parliament.gov.sg/mp/pritam-singh?viewcv=Pritam Mr Pritam Singh] {{Wayback|url=http://www.parliament.gov.sg/mp/pritam-singh?viewcv=Pritam |date=20150924085516 }}, parliament.gov.sg, retrieved 6 April 2012.</ref>。自2018年起，毕丹星從[[劉程強|劉程強]]手中接過工人黨秘書長一職，並在2020年起出任[[新加坡國會反對黨領袖|官方反對黨領袖]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=GE2020: Election results a clear mandate for PAP but also reflects desire for more diversity of voices in Parliament, says PM {{!}} The Straits Times|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/politics/pm-lee-pap-will-designate-pritam-as-opposition-leader-urges-all-sporeans-to-put-aside|access-date=2021-12-23|date=2020-07-11|last=Auto|first=Hermes|work=www.straitstimes.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711092648/https://www.straitstimes.com/politics/pm-lee-pap-will-designate-pritam-as-opposition-leader-urges-all-sporeans-to-put-aside|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 早年教育 ==
毕丹星曾就讀於伍茲維爾小學、麗城小學、聖托馬斯中學和裕廊初級學院。他入讀[[新加坡国立大学|新加坡國立大學]]文學暨社會科學院，1999年他於歷史與政治學的兩個科目取得最佳成績，獲頒Straits Steamship Prize榮譽，並於2000年以歷史文學學士學位畢業。<ref>{{Cite web|title=畢丹星十年磨一劍 新加坡工人黨考驗剛開始 {{!}} 國際 {{!}} 中央社 CNA|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202007150225.aspx|access-date=2021-12-14|author=黃自強|date=2020-07-15|work=www.cna.com.tw|publisher=中央社|language=zh-TW|quote="....最後獲悉錄取新加坡國立大學文學暨社會科學院，心情簡直像中彩券一樣。/1999年他於歷史與政治學的兩個科目取得最佳成績，獲頒Straits Steamship Prize榮譽。2000年取得歷史榮譽學位。"|archive-date=2021-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211214231056/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202007150225.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Exclusive Interview with Pritam Singh, Univantage, [[Singapore_Management_University|SMU]], October 2011</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=这里是否留下你的光辉岁月？|url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/singapore/story20170420-751121|access-date=2020-03-11|date=2017-04-20|last=林佳憓|first=文 /|website=早报|language=zh-Hans|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191109115731/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/singapore/story20170420-751121|archive-date=9 November 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>他其後獲得了獎學金，前往倫敦國王學院攻讀研究生，並於2004年獲得了文學碩士學位。<ref>[http://ukinsingapore.fco.gov.uk/en/visiting-uk/studying-in-uk/our-scholarships/015chevening-04Aug2011 2011's Chevening Scholars] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20120718161411/http://ukinsingapore.fco.gov.uk/en/visiting-uk/studying-in-uk/our-scholarships/015chevening-04Aug2011|date=18 July 2012}}, British High Commission Singapore website, retrieved 8 April 2012.</ref><ref>[http://www.kcl.ac.uk/sspp/departments/warstudies/people/alumni/news.aspx News from our alumni] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825174639/http://www.kcl.ac.uk/sspp/departments/warstudies/people/alumni/news.aspx|date=25 August 2012}}, kcl.ac.uk, retrieved 8 April 2012.</ref>他還在2005年時獲得了[[馬來西亞國際伊斯蘭大學|馬來西亞國際伊斯蘭大學]]的伊斯蘭研究文憑。<ref>[http://wp.sg/wpge/candidates/pritam-singh-2/ Pritam Singh] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110626121923/http://wp.sg/wpge/candidates/pritam-singh-2/|date=26 June 2011}}, wp.sg, retrieved 6 April 2012.</ref>

== 事業 ==

=== 軍旅生涯 ===
毕丹星在1994年加入[[新加坡武裝部隊|新加坡武裝部隊]]，並於1997年至2002年擔任職業委任軍官。在服役期間，他是一名野戰工程師。<ref>{{cite web|title=‘Loss of fellow NSman hits close to home’: WP’s Pritam Singh on Aloysius Pang’s death|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/singapore/pritam-singh-aloysius-pang-death-tribute-nsman-909036|access-date=10 December 2021|date=24 January 2019|website=CNA|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210204436/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/singapore/pritam-singh-aloysius-pang-death-tribute-nsman-909036|dead-url=no}}</ref>目前，他是一名預備役指揮官，軍銜為少校。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Workers’ Party’s new Secretary-General: 10 things to know about Pritam Singh - Channel NewsAsia|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180408095821/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/workers-party-secretary-general-pritam-singh-10-things-to-know-10116750|access-date=2021-12-14|date=2018-04-08|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>

=== 政治生涯 ===

==== 成為國會議員 ====
在[[2011年新加坡大选|2011年新加坡大選]]期間，毕丹星是[[工人黨_(新加坡)|工人黨]]在[[阿裕尼集选区|阿裕尼集選區]]競選的五人團體之一。該團隊包括黨秘書長[[刘程强|劉程強]]、黨主席[[林瑞莲|林瑞蓮]]、成員[[陳碩茂|陳碩茂]]和穆罕默德·馬納普(Muhamad Faisal bin Abdul Manap)。他們以54.71%得票率，擊敗得票率45.29％的執政黨[[人民行動黨|人民行動黨]]候選人，是新加坡歷史上第一次有反對黨在集選區勝出<ref>{{Cite web|title=新加坡大选：台湾出生律师披上反对党战衣|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world_commentary/2011/05/110507_singapore_voting_day|access-date=2021-12-14|date=2011-05-07|work=BBC News 中文|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2021-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211214224548/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world_commentary/2011/05/110507_singapore_voting_day|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他其後被任命為工人黨執行委員會的助理秘書長。<ref>[http://wp.sg/our-organisation/executive-council/ Executive Council] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728110917/http://wp.sg/our-organisation/executive-council/|date=28 July 2013}} , wp.sg, retrieved 6 April 2012.</ref>

==== 領導工人黨 ====
2017年工人黨秘書長劉程強宣布退休，希望新血能振興黨，而毕丹星被廣泛認為是下一任工人黨主席。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/politics/pritam-singh-tipped-to-be-next-wp-chief|title=Pritam Singh tipped to be next WP chief|date=14 November 2017|work=The Straits Times|access-date=2017-12-10|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211055326/http://www.straitstimes.com/politics/pritam-singh-tipped-to-be-next-wp-chief|archive-date=2017-12-11|url-status=live}}</ref>

毕丹星於2018年4月8日劉程強卸任後接任工人黨秘書長一職。由於[[工人黨_(新加坡)|工人黨]]是[[新加坡國會|議會]]中唯一有席位的反對黨，因此他也成為事實上的反對黨領袖。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/pritam-singh-elected-new-wp-chief-succeeding-low-thia-khiang-10116736|title=Pritam Singh elected new WP chief, succeeding Low Thia Khiang|work=Channel NewsAsia|access-date=2018-04-29|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180408110827/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/pritam-singh-elected-new-wp-chief-succeeding-low-thia-khiang-10116736|archive-date=2018-04-08|url-status=live}}</ref>

==== 2020年新加坡大選 ====
在2020年新加坡大選中，毕丹星與林瑞蓮、陳碩茂、嚴燕松及萊昂·佩雷拉(Leon Perera)再次在阿裕尼集選區當選，這次得票率上升至59.95%，擊敗了獲得40.05%得票率的人民行動黨候選人團隊。<ref name="CNAAljunied">{{cite news|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/ge2020-workers-party-retains-aljunied-grc-12922390|title=GE2020: Workers' Party retains Aljunied GRC with wider margin against PAP|author=Chew Hui Min|work=Channel News Asia|date=11 June 2020|access-date=4 April 2021|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420092919/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/ge2020-workers-party-retains-aljunied-grc-12922390|dead-url=no}}</ref>工人黨還贏得[[後港單選區|後港單選區]]及新設立的[[盛港集選區|盛港集選區]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/ge2020-workers-party-retains-hougang-smc-with-61-19-of-votes-12922396|title=GE2020: Workers' Party retains Hougang SMC with 61.19% of votes|last=Yeoh|first=Grace|work=Channel News Asia|date=11 July 2020|access-date=4 April 2021|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716035952/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/ge2020-workers-party-retains-hougang-smc-with-61-19-of-votes-12922396|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNAAljunied2">{{cite news|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/ge2020-workers-party-retains-aljunied-grc-12922390|title=GE2020: Workers' Party retains Aljunied GRC with wider margin against PAP|author=Chew Hui Min|work=Channel News Asia|date=11 June 2020|access-date=4 April 2021|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420092919/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/ge2020-workers-party-retains-aljunied-grc-12922390|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 官方反對黨領袖 ====
在工人黨贏得10個席位後，總理李顯龍決定正式任命毕丹星為反對黨領袖，並表示將向他提供適當的支持和資源，來讓他履行新的職責。<ref>{{Cite web|title=PM Lee Hsien Loong on GE2020 results: 'We have a clear mandate'|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BlhusR7McMg|access-date=11 July 2020|website=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712020524/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BlhusR7McMg|archive-date=12 July 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title=GE2020: Election results a clear mandate for PAP but also reflects desire for more diversity of voices in Parliament, says PM|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/politics/pm-lee-pap-will-designate-pritam-as-opposition-leader-urges-all-sporeans-to-put-aside|newspaper=The Straits Times|date=2020-07-11|accessdate=2021-12-14|issn=0585-3923|language=en|first=Royston|last=Sim|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711092648/https://www.straitstimes.com/politics/pm-lee-pap-will-designate-pritam-as-opposition-leader-urges-all-sporeans-to-put-aside|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=观察家：毕丹星被点名反对党领袖 行动党或为国会两党制铺路 {{!}} 早报|url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/special/report/singapore/singapore-13th-ge/analysis-and-commentary/story20200712-1068412|access-date=2021-12-15|work=www.zaobao.com.sg|language=zh-Hans|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215001201/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/special/report/singapore/singapore-13th-ge/analysis-and-commentary/story20200712-1068412|dead-url=no}}</ref>在此之前，因為憲法沒有規定這樣的職位，所以反對黨領袖在議會中是一個非正式的職位。他的年薪為也提升到385,000新加坡元，是普通議員工資的兩倍。<ref>{{Cite web|title=WP's Pritam Singh clarifies he will donate half his salary increase as Opposition Leader, not half his entire salary|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/politics/wp-chief-pritam-singh-clarifies-that-he-will-donate-half-his-salary-increase-not-half-his|date=1 August 2020|website=The Straits Times|access-date=2021-12-14|archive-date=2021-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211212131017/https://www.straitstimes.com/politics/wp-chief-pritam-singh-clarifies-that-he-will-donate-half-his-salary-increase-not-half-his|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 其他事業 ===
